      "id": 1,
      "type": 2,
      "origin": 3,
      "description": "*Bom dia,Gostaria de saber os valores de vocês para passagem\r\naérea e estadia para o período de 15 a 17, com saída de Florianópolis.Fico\r\nno aguardo do retorno.*\r\n*Viviane C. Moraes*\r\n48 - 999271965\r\n",
      "htmlDescription": "<div dir=\"auto\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\"><i style=\"border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\"><div style=\"font-size: inherit\"><p style=\"font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0; text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\"><span>Bom dia,</span></p><p style=\"font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0; text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\">Gostaria de saber os valores de vocês para&nbsp;<span>passagem aérea</span>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<span>estadia</span>&nbsp;para o período de&nbsp;<span>15 a 17</span>, com&nbsp;<span>saída de Florianópolis</span>.</p><p style=\"font-style: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0; text-decoration: none; font-size: inherit; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\" dir=\"auto\">Fico no aguardo do retorno.<br></p></div><br></i></span></div><div dir=\"auto\"><b style=\"border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\"><i style=\"border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1)\">Viviane C. Moraes</i></b><br clear=\"all\"></div><div dir=\"auto\"><div dir=\"auto\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><div>48 - 999271965</div><div><a href=\"https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/mail-sig/AIorK4zwameZWR5KJsRLqBzNcHPuUh8f5WtaqOiDCEZ-Eru0vTS6Hbsoa2SjllveO78MO-OFxeoICsm3YbXr\" data-original-href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"colorbox\"><img width=\"96\" height=\"50\" style=\"font-size: 12.8px\" src=\"https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/mail-sig/AIorK4zwameZWR5KJsRLqBzNcHPuUh8f5WtaqOiDCEZ-Eru0vTS6Hbsoa2SjllveO78MO-OFxeoICsm3YbXr\"></a><br></div></div></div></div></div>\n",
